But, for now, this room's secure.

28
00:02:16,198 --> 00:02:18,365
好的 电话也安全吗
Good. Phones, too?

29
00:02:18,367 --> 00:02:19,733
呃 别用座机
Uh, don't use landlines.

30
00:02:19,735 --> 00:02:21,468
但如果你的助理发现 听筒里有回音或敲击声
But make sure your assistant lets you know

31
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:22,969
让她一定要告诉你
if she hears any echoes or clicks.

32
00:02:22,971 --> 00:02:24,471
有可能是线路窃听
Could mean a wiretap.

33
00:02:24,473 --> 00:02:26,506
如果真的是窃听 我们应该可以追查到源头
And, if so, we should be able to trace its source.

34
00:02:26,508 --> 00:02:27,874
手机呢 没问题吗
What about cell phones-- they good?

35
00:02:27,876 --> 00:02:29,242
手机没问题
Cell's good.

36
00:02:29,244 --> 00:02:32,412
好的 那我们也没问题了
All right. We're good, then.

37
00:02:32,414 --> 00:02:33,880
两千 是吗
2,000, right?

38
00:02:33,882 --> 00:02:35,615
不必了 我们会给你寄账单
Uh, that's okay, we'll just bill you.

39
00:02:35,617 --> 00:02:37,050
不 不行
Uh, no. No, no.

40
00:02:37,052 --> 00:02:38,451
不要账单
No bills.

41
00:02:38,453 --> 00:02:40,553
这事只有你我知道 明白吗
It's between us, you understand?

42
00:02:40,555 --> 00:02:41,755
明白了
Understood.

43
00:02:41,757 --> 00:02:43,690
好的
Okay.

44
00:02:49,264 --> 00:02:51,331
-你好 -Frank 我是Hamilton
- Hello? - Frank, it's Hamilton.

45
00:02:51,333 --> 00:02:53,066
你确定这条线没问题吗
Are you sure this line is secure?

46
00:02:53,068 --> 00:02:54,768
说实话 我现在对什么都不确定了
Honestly, I'm not sure about anything anymore.

47
00:02:54,770 --> 00:02:56,469
让我非常困扰
Gotten in pretty deep here.

48
00:02:56,471 --> 00:02:58,905
你也不该感到确定 市长先生 因为我
Nor should you be, Mr. Mayor, 'cause I'm gonna be

49
00:02:58,907 --> 00:03:00,840
就站在你跟前 宝贝儿
up and in your grill, baby.

50
00:03:00,842 --> 00:03:03,977
他都清理过手机了 我们怎么还能窃听他
How can we still hear him if they swept his cell?

51
00:03:03,979 --> 00:03:07,447
你是无法清理3P的影子应用的
You can't sweep a Triple P shadow app,

52
00:03:07,449 --> 00:03:09,983
这个应用让我能窃听并录下
which allows me to listen to and record

53
00:03:09,985 --> 00:03:12,953
听得见的任何声音
any and everything within earshot.

54
00:03:12,955 --> 00:03:15,055
问题在于 不是所有事情
Problem is, anything and everything isn't covered

55
00:03:15,057 --> 00:03:16,690
都在窃听令的许可范围
under the wiretap warrant.

56
00:03:16,692 --> 00:03:18,491
只能是关于清水市
Only what's related to Clearwater

57
00:03:18,493 --> 00:03:20,727
或者他所谓的海外行贿基金
or his alleged offshore slush funds.

58
00:03:20,729 --> 00:03:22,062
还有Javier Garcia的谋杀案
And Javier Garcia's murder.

59
00:03:22,064 --> 00:03:23,530
告诉Jess
Let Jess know,

60
00:03:23,532 --> 00:03:26,066
我这段时间不能见她了
uh, I won't be seeing her for a while.

61
00:03:26,068 --> 00:03:28,868
不能冒险让媒体再挖出什么绯闻了
Can't risk the media finding out about any more of these affairs.

62
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:31,705
-停止录音 -等等 什么
- Stop recording. - Wait, what?

63
00:03:31,707 --> 00:03:33,239
私人信息
Personal information is not covered

64
00:03:33,241 --> 00:03:35,075
不在窃听范围之内
under the scope of the wiretap.

65
00:03:35,077 --> 00:03:37,744
听着 Dwayne 如果不能严格按照要求执行
Look, Dwayne, if this isn't done within the strict parameters

66
00:03:37,746 --> 00:03:39,813
在法庭上是站不住脚的
of the order, it won't stand up in court.

67
00:03:39,815 --> 00:03:42,048
市长并不干净 Karen
Mayor's dirty, Karen.

68
00:03:42,050 --> 00:03:44,484
Rita让这个案子正式成立了
Look, Rita's put together a solid circumstantial case,

69
00:03:44,486 --> 00:03:47,153
但是Jenkins... 他是唯一一个愿意
but Jenkins-- he was the only judge willing to risk

70
00:03:47,155 --> 00:03:50,156
冒险跟Hamilton对立 同意窃听的法官
going up against Hamilton to grant the tap.

71
00:03:50,158 --> 00:03:52,158
我知道你们有多想扳倒他
I know how bad you want to take him down,

72
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,994
但如果你们不按法律条文办事
but if you don't do this by the book,

73
00:03:53,996 --> 00:03:55,362
你们会失去窃听许可
you're gonna blow the wiretap.

74
00:03:55,364 --> 00:03:57,630
Hamilton就会从谋杀案脱身
And Hamilton gets away with murder.

75
00:03:57,632 --> 00:03:59,666
还有其它案件
And everything else.

76
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:03,136
停止录音
Stop recording.

77
00:04:06,108 --> 00:04:08,174
好了 我有案子了
Ah, all right, I got a case.

78
00:04:08,176 --> 00:04:09,843
继续监视市长
Keep monitoring the mayor.

79
00:04:09,845 --> 00:04:12,479
你确定Patton知道监听的关键字吗
Are you sure Patton knows what keywords to listen for?

80
00:04:12,481 --> 00:04:13,980
他知道清水市案子的
Is he read in on Clearwater,

81
00:04:13,982 --> 00:04:15,482
全部细节了吗
every detail?

82
00:04:15,484 --> 00:04:17,350
不 不是全部
No, not everything.

83
00:04:17,352 --> 00:04:19,786
那我要是你 我会待在这里
Then I'd stay put if I were you.

84
00:04:19,788 --> 00:04:22,155
拿下Hamilton可能只有这一次机会
May only get this one shot at Hamilton.

85
00:04:32,134 --> 00:04:35,035
Pride还好吗 他听起来怎么样
Yeah, is Pride all right? How'd he sound?

86
00:04:35,037 --> 00:04:36,569
纠结
Torn.

87
00:04:36,571 --> 00:04:38,004
必须说服他待在那里
Had to talk him into staying put,

88
00:04:38,006 --> 00:04:39,339
集中精力扳倒Hamilton
focusing on trying to get Hamilton

89
00:04:39,341 --> 00:04:40,640
在他干掉我们之前
before Hamilton gets us.

90
00:04:40,642 --> 00:04:42,442
是啊 King对工作很忠诚
Yeah, King's loyal to the job.

91
00:04:42,444 --> 00:04:45,345
让他放弃主导案件侦破很不容易
It's not easy for him not taking the lead on a case.

92
00:04:45,347 --> 00:04:47,147
所以我们更要把这个案子办得漂漂亮亮
All the more reason for us to kick ass on this one.

93
00:04:47,149 --> 00:04:48,615
你要我去接Percy吗
Do you want me to go pick up Percy?

94
00:04:48,617 --> 00:04:51,117
不用 我已经在咖啡店这里了
No, I'm already here at the coffee shop.

95
00:04:51,119 --> 00:04:53,086
我们一会儿在犯罪...
We'll meet you at the crime...

96
00:04:54,122 --> 00:04:56,089
现场见
...scene.

97
00:04:57,826 --> 00:04:59,859
Lasalle
Lasalle?

98
00:05:01,129 --> 00:05:02,796
Lasalle 你还在吗
Lasalle, you still there?

99
00:05:02,798 --> 00:05:05,065
是 我还在
Yeah, I'm still here.

100
00:05:05,067 --> 00:05:06,633
一会见
We'll see you in a bit.

101
00:05:06,635 --> 00:05:08,535
嗨
Hey!

102
00:05:08,537 --> 00:05:10,036
乡下鼠
Country Mouse.

103
00:05:10,038 --> 00:05:11,504
早知道是你来接我
If I knew you were my ride,

104
00:05:11,506 --> 00:05:13,440
我会给你带个羊角面包
I would've picked you up a croissant.

105
00:05:16,645 --> 00:05:17,677
一切还好吗
Everything all right?

106
00:05:17,679 --> 00:05:20,747
当然 我们出发吧
Yeah, sure. Let's roll.

107
00:05:33,061 --> 00:05:34,961
嘿 你确定没什么心事吗
Hey, you sure nothing's bothering you?

108
00:05:34,963 --> 00:05:36,796
我吗 没啊 怎么了
Me? No, why?

109
00:05:36,798 --> 00:05:38,498
我不知道 也许是因为这一路上
I don't know, maybe 'cause you only said, like,

110
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,533
你只跟我说了两个字
two words to me on the way over.

111
00:05:40,535 --> 00:05:42,268
是我哎 怎么回事
Come on, it's me. What?

112
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,603
Gregorio 我们掌握了什么
Gregorio, what do we got?

113
00:05:43,605 --> 00:05:44,938
你也好啊 Christopher
Hello to you, too, Christopher.

114
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:46,573
哦 姐们儿 他心情不太好
Oh, girl, he is in a mood.

115
00:05:46,575 --> 00:05:48,541
看得出来
I can see that.

116
00:05:48,543 --> 00:05:50,043
抢劫团伙很专业
Heist crew were pros,

117
00:05:50,045 --> 00:05:51,845
干掉了监控 阻断了通讯
took out cameras, jammed communication,

118
00:05:51,847 --> 00:05:54,114
很清楚地知道他们想要的东西是什么 在哪里
knew exactly what they were after and where to get it.

119
00:05:54,116 --> 00:05:55,849
Sebastian 货物是什么
Sebastian, what's the haul?

120
00:05:55,851 --> 00:05:57,884
运往Fort Bragg基地的几百个MP5冲锋枪
Couple hundred MP5s headed to Fort Bragg.

121
00:05:57,886 --> 00:05:59,519
海军还在清查库存
The Navy's still doing an inventory

122
00:05:59,521 --> 00:06:01,187
以获知准确数目 不过...
to get an exact count, but...

123
00:06:01,189 --> 00:06:03,656
那可是大批量的重火力武器
That's a lot of serious firepower.

124
00:06:03,658 --> 00:06:05,892
我是说 这不可能只是为了
I mean, this can't just be about selling them

125
00:06:05,894 --> 00:06:07,360
到黑市上去卖吧
on the black market.

126
00:06:07,362 --> 00:06:09,062
我们遇到了民兵组织之类的吗
We're dealing with some kind of militia?

127
00:06:09,064 --> 00:06:11,064
不管他们是谁 都是有备而来的
Well, whoever it was, they came prepared.

128
00:06:11,066 --> 00:06:13,867
根据铁路警察的说法 他们都有防弹衣
According to the railway cops, they all had body armor,

129
00:06:13,869 --> 00:06:15,969
用的是AR-15突击步枪 震荡手雷
were using AR-15s, concussive grenades.

130
00:06:15,971 --> 00:06:17,337
有多少人受伤
How many were injured?

131
00:06:17,339 --> 00:06:18,571
怪就怪在这儿 没人受伤
That's the thing-- none.

132
00:06:18,573 --> 00:06:22,475
哇 抢劫团伙用了AR-15突击步枪 手雷
Whoa. Heist crew using AR-15s, grenades,

133
00:06:22,477 --> 00:06:26,045
带着MP5冲锋枪逃跑 竟然没一个警察中枪
making off with MP5s, and no cop gets shot?

134
00:06:26,047 --> 00:06:28,381
不 警察们被射击了 但射中他们的不是子弹
Oh, no, cops were shot all right, just not with bullets.

135
00:06:28,383 --> 00:06:29,749
没错 不是致命的子弹
Yeah, not with lethal rounds.

136
00:06:29,751 --> 00:06:31,117
而是橡胶子弹
With rubber bullets.

137
00:06:31,119 --> 00:06:32,352
专门设计的复合材料
Specifically designed composite,

138
00:06:32,354 --> 00:06:33,686
就像中了一记重拳一样
packs a heck of a punch,

139
00:06:33,688 --> 00:06:35,221
尤其是用AR-15射出来
especially coming out of an AR-15.

140
00:06:35,223 --> 00:06:37,190
能打得你喘不过气来
It's more than enough to knock the wind out of you.

141
00:06:37,192 --> 00:06:39,259
-但不会死人 -那么问题来了
- But not kill. - Which begs the question,

142
00:06:39,261 --> 00:06:41,461
什么样的抢劫团伙 去偷上百个致命武器
what kind of heist crew steals hundreds of lethal weapons

143
00:06:41,463 --> 00:06:43,129
会带非致命武器呢
using nonlethal rounds?

144
00:06:43,131 --> 00:06:44,531
是啊 这说不通
Yeah. Doesn't make sense.

145
00:06:44,533 --> 00:06:45,899
是的 但幸亏铁路警察
Yeah, well, fortunately the rail cops

146
00:06:45,901 --> 00:06:47,534
用的是真子弹
were using live ammo.

147
00:06:49,237 --> 00:06:50,570
他们打中了一个团伙成员
They tagged one of the crew.

148
00:06:50,572 --> 00:06:53,173
流了不少血 我应该能通过DNA查明身份
Lost a lot of blood. I should be able to get a DNA I.D.

149
00:06:53,175 --> 00:06:54,908
好的 有发现就告诉我们 Sebastian
All right, let us know what you find, Sebastian.

150
00:06:54,910 --> 00:06:56,976
那个有钱人是谁
Who's the fat cat?

151
00:06:57,946 --> 00:06:59,946
枪支制造公司的老板
Owner of the company that makes the guns,

152
00:06:59,948 --> 00:07:01,181
Justus Bancroft
Justus Bancroft.

153
00:07:01,183 --> 00:07:02,715
或者说是受害者
Or the victim.

154
00:07:02,717 --> 00:07:05,418
慢着 在ATF里待了那么多年
Whoa. Spent a lot of years at ATF

155
00:07:02,717 --> 00:07:05,418
{\a6}烟酒、火器与爆炸物管理局

156
00:07:05,420 --> 00:07:07,987
看过Bancroft的枪械产品所造成的伤害
seeing the pain Bancroft guns cause.

157
00:07:07,989 --> 00:07:10,190
很难把他们当成受害人
Hardly makes them a victim.

158
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,626
打扰一下
Excuse me.

159
00:07:13,628 --> 00:07:16,863
海军罪案调查处 可以和我聊聊吗
NCIS. Mind if I get a word?

160
00:07:16,865 --> 00:07:19,032
不好意思 请问有什么问题吗
Sorry, is there a problem?

161
00:07:19,034 --> 00:07:21,134
不 当然没问题
No, no, no, not at all.

162
00:07:21,136 --> 00:07:22,635
只是 呃
It's just that, uh, well,

163
00:07:22,637 --> 00:07:24,604
我们已经把知道的都告诉警察了
we already told the police everything we know.

164
00:07:24,606 --> 00:07:26,139
而且我们必须走了
And we have to go.

165
00:07:26,141 --> 00:07:28,374
抱歉 请问你是
I'm sorry, who are you?

166
00:07:28,376 --> 00:07:29,809
Nadine
Nadine.

167
00:07:29,811 --> 00:07:31,244
Bancroft
Bancroft.

168
00:07:32,547 --> 00:07:35,148
特别探员Lasalle
Special Agent Lasalle.

169
00:07:35,150 --> 00:07:37,483
我们之后会和警方沟通 但如果你不介意的话...
We'll talk with NOPD afterwards, but if you don't mind...

170
00:07:37,485 --> 00:07:41,120
当然不介意 尽管问
No, no, of course, of course. Ask me anything.

171
00:07:41,122 --> 00:07:43,156
只不过 呃 我们明天
Well, it's just that, uh, we're hosting

172
00:07:43,158 --> 00:07:44,958
要举办年度慈善活动
our annual charity event tomorrow.

173
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:48,761
我倒是觉得几百支冲锋枪不知所踪
I kind of think a couple hundred missing submachine guns

174
00:07:48,763 --> 00:07:50,964
比你们的小派对更重要 不是吗
trumps your little party, don't you?

175
00:07:50,966 --> 00:07:52,065
Percy
Percy.

176
00:07:53,001 --> 00:07:54,901
无意冒犯 但是
No disrespect, but, uh,

177
00:07:54,903 --> 00:07:57,470
我们的工作还是要做的 而且枪支数量很多
we got to do our jobs, and that's a lot of guns.

178
00:07:57,472 --> 00:07:59,072
对 相信我 我理解
Oh, yeah, trust me, I know.

179
00:07:59,074 --> 00:08:01,040
这也不是我们第一次遭遇这种事了
It's not the first time we've been hit, either.

180
00:08:01,042 --> 00:08:02,275
你们以前也被抢劫过
You've been robbed before?

181
00:08:02,277 --> 00:08:04,911
没有这么严重 但是有过
Well, not to this extent, but yes.

182
00:08:04,913 --> 00:08:06,980
FBI ATF 他们都
Uh, the FBI, ATF, they both investigated

183
00:08:06,982 --> 00:08:09,349
调查过前两次抢劫 但无功而返
the other two times, and, uh, come up empty.

184
00:08:09,351 --> 00:08:11,784
我很高兴没有警察受伤
I'm just glad none of the police got hurt.

185
00:08:11,786 --> 00:08:14,520
三次 这里面一定有什么联系
Well, third time, there's got to be a connection.

