224
00:09:32,634 --> 00:09:33,933
这怎么可能呢
How's that possible?

225
00:09:33,935 --> 00:09:35,401
更奇怪的是 以前被偷的枪
Even stranger, none of the past stolen guns

226
00:09:35,403 --> 00:09:37,003
