如果你一直对我采取沉默的方式
If you're gonna keep giving me the silent treatment

253
00:10:35,163 --> 00:10:36,629
来折磨我
and being mean to me...

254
00:10:36,631 --> 00:10:38,097
我没折磨你
I'm not being mean to you.

255
00:10:38,099 --> 00:10:40,566
好吧 那是怎么回事
Okay, so what's your problem?

256
00:10:40,568 --> 00:10:42,802
我不明白
I don't understand.

257
00:10:42,804 --> 00:10:45,004
我就是对今早的事情很吃惊
I was just surprised this morning,

258
00:10:45,006 --> 00:10:47,673
看到你和那个人在咖啡馆
seeing you with that guy at the coffee shop.

259
00:10:47,675 --> 00:10:50,343
等等 Tom吗
Wait, Tom?

260
00:10:50,345 --> 00:10:52,245
我不知道你在跟人约会
I didn't know you were dating anybody.

261
00:10:52,247 --> 00:10:54,647
我没在约会
I'm not dating anybody.

262
00:10:54,649 --> 00:10:56,082
只是喝咖啡而已
It was just coffee.

263
00:10:56,084 --> 00:10:57,784
再说 我一点都不了解他
Besides, I barely know that guy.

264
00:10:57,786 --> 00:10:59,819
你已经了解到可以亲他了
Well, you knew him well enough to kiss him.

265
00:10:59,821 --> 00:11:02,422
我没亲他 是他亲的我
I didn't kiss-- he kissed me.

266
00:11:05,593 --> 00:11:06,993
你是在吃醋吗
Are you jealous?

267
00:11:06,995 --> 00:11:08,694
吃醋
Jealous.

268
00:11:08,696 --> 00:11:10,663
-你吃醋了 -你发什么疯呢
- You're jealous. - You're trippin' girl.

269
00:11:10,665 --> 00:11:13,099
快点 准备武器
Come on. Let's gear up.

270
00:11:25,847 --> 00:11:28,114
散弹枪 不是吧
Shotguns? Really?

271
00:11:28,116 --> 00:11:29,715
受伤的陆战队员
Yeah, wounded Marine.

272
00:11:29,717 --> 00:11:32,418
她手里应该有一把MP5冲锋枪
She's probably armed with a MP5 by now.

273
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:34,187
还是小心点好
Better safe than sorry.

274
00:11:37,225 --> 00:11:39,225
联邦探员
Federal agents!

275
00:11:44,199 --> 00:11:45,898
Percy
Percy.

276
00:11:52,907 --> 00:11:55,808
这不可能只是抢劫中的枪
No way that's just from the heist shooting.

277
00:12:05,193 --> 00:12:07,393
街对面的房子装有安全监控
House across the street has a security camera,

278
00:12:07,395 --> 00:12:09,161
但摄像头的角度难以确定
but it's a bad angle to I.D. anyone

279
00:12:09,163 --> 00:12:11,197
进出Bellacroix房子的人的身份
going in and out of Bellacroix's place.

280
00:12:11,199 --> 00:12:14,233
所以没人拿着MP5冲锋枪走出来吗
Ooh, so no one walking out with an MP5?

281
00:12:14,235 --> 00:12:16,435
有个拿着小包的女士 就这样
Lady carrying a small bag. That's about it.

282
00:12:16,437 --> 00:12:17,703
这看起来越来越像
It's looking more and more like

283
00:12:17,705 --> 00:12:19,605
那个团伙为了掩盖踪迹干掉了她
the crew took her out to cover their tracks.

284
00:12:19,607 --> 00:12:22,542
找个凶狠的家伙把自己人干掉
Takes a pretty vicious crew to take out one of their own.

285
00:12:22,544 --> 00:12:23,809
我们得查出他们是谁
We need to find out who they are

286
00:12:23,811 --> 00:12:25,811
这样才能尽快找回那些枪
so we can get those guns back, fast.

287
00:12:25,813 --> 00:12:28,114
问题是 他们在掩盖行踪上做得太好了
The problem is, they're so good at covering their tracks,

288
00:12:28,116 --> 00:12:29,582
我们什么都没查到
we got squat.

289
00:12:29,584 --> 00:12:33,052
要是我们能查清楚 一开始是什么让一个光荣的陆战队员
Yeah. If we could just figure out what made a decorated Marine

290
00:12:33,054 --> 00:12:35,121
加入一个抢劫团伙
join a heist crew in the first place.

291
00:12:35,123 --> 00:12:37,123
你确定在她的服役记录中
Are you sure there weren't any red flags

292
00:12:37,125 --> 00:12:38,324
没有任何危险信号吗
in her service record?

293
00:12:38,326 --> 00:12:40,359
没有创伤后应激障碍 没有心理恐慌
No PTSD, no psych alarm.

294
00:12:40,361 --> 00:12:43,262
她的同事中是否有犯罪记录
Any of her known associates with criminal backgrounds?

