00:12:43,264 --> 00:12:44,699
没有 Bellacroix是新奥尔良本地人
No. Bellacroix's a NOLA native,

296
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:46,699
路易斯安那州立大学研究生 名列前茅
LSU grad, top of her class.

297
00:12:46,701 --> 00:12:48,434
说了吧 什么都查不到
Like I said, squat.

298
00:12:48,436 --> 00:12:52,305
听我说 我知道监听Hamilton比什么都重要
Look, I know the Hamilton wire is important and everything,

299
00:12:52,307 --> 00:12:54,574
但也许是时候让Pride参与进来了
but think maybe it's time to loop Pride in?

300
00:12:54,576 --> 00:12:58,077
King希望我们能找到线索
King's expecting us to find leads.

301
00:13:00,081 --> 00:13:01,347
继续调查吧
Let's keep digging.

302
00:13:01,349 --> 00:13:03,716
好吧
All right.

