00:13:40,188 --> 00:13:41,420
去杀自己人吗
to kill one of their own?

320
00:13:41,422 --> 00:13:44,023
或许他们知道 杀警察会被判处死刑
Maybe they knew killing cops guarantees the needle.

321
00:13:44,025 --> 00:13:47,059
但如果他们把其中一把枪变成了杀人凶器
Yeah, but if any of those guns end up as the murder weapon,

322
00:13:47,061 --> 00:13:48,327
