and any one of them would've sufficed.

340
00:14:21,562 --> 00:14:25,297
这显然是一起声明性的谋杀
This was obviously a statement killing.

341
00:14:25,299 --> 00:14:27,767
好让其他成员乖乖听话
One way to keep the rest of the crew in line.

342
00:14:27,769 --> 00:14:29,535
但是 有一个异常
However, there is an anomaly.

343
00:14:29,537 --> 00:14:32,071
在Bellacroix女士被杀之前
Before Ms. Bellacroix was murdered,

344
00:14:32,073 --> 00:14:34,840
有人缝合了她在抢劫时
someone sutured the initial gunshot wound

345
00:14:34,842 --> 00:14:36,676
由铁路警察造成的
inflicted by the railway officer

346
00:14:36,678 --> 00:14:38,144
初始枪伤
during the heist.

347
00:14:38,146 --> 00:14:39,679
甚至取出了子弹
Even removed the bullet.

348
00:14:39,681 --> 00:14:42,915
等等 他们要杀她 为什么还要救她
Wait, why would they try to save her only to kill her?

349
00:14:42,917 --> 00:14:44,417
这根本说不通啊
That doesn't make any sense.

350
00:14:44,419 --> 00:14:46,952
尤其是当你知道 他们还给她
Especially when you factor in that they gave her

