00:40:02,115 --> 00:40:04,148
和Percy探员在法庭上的证词相违背
Agent Percy's statement to the court.

894
00:40:04,150 --> 00:40:05,650
你撒谎了
You lied.

895
00:40:05,652 --> 00:40:07,485
没有 是这样
No. See...

896
00:40:07,487 --> 00:40:10,355
当时队伍正处在枪战之中 我...
the team was in the middle of a firefight. I...

897
00:40:10,357 --> 00:40:12,657
你在你宣誓过的证词中
You said in your sworn statement,

898
00:40:12,659 --> 00:40:15,894
是这么说的"Nadine Bancroft逃跑了"
and I quote, “Nadine Bancroft got away.”

899
00:40:15,896 --> 00:40:19,330
明显地 你本可以在那个时候逮捕她
Clearly, you could have arrested her right then and there.

900
00:40:19,332 --> 00:40:21,165
在你回到队伍之前 把她逮捕
Cuffed her before you went back in.

901
00:40:21,167 --> 00:40:23,668
我担心我的队伍
I was worried about my team.

902
00:40:25,338 --> 00:40:26,838
我做了主观决定
I made a judgment call.

903
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,139
你让一个重罪犯逃跑了
You let a felon escape.

904
00:40:28,141 --> 00:40:30,875
好的 等等
Okay, hold on.

905
00:40:30,877 --> 00:40:33,945
单纯出于好奇
Just out of curiosity...

906
00:40:33,947 --> 00:40:36,214
是什么让你去看监控的
what made you think to look for surveillance?

907
00:40:36,216 --> 00:40:37,515
这不是重点
That's not the point.

908
00:40:37,517 --> 00:40:39,684
这更像是报复而不是追求正义
It is if this is more about retribution than justice.

909
00:40:40,820 --> 00:40:42,620
你是在宽恕你探员的行为吗 Pride探员
Are you condoning your agent's behavior, Agent Pride?

910
00:40:42,622 --> 00:40:45,556
我不宽恕以莫须有罪名进行政治迫害
I'm not condoning a witch hunt, if that's what you're asking.

911
00:40:45,558 --> 00:40:47,992
你俩到底在说什么
What the hell are you two talking about?

912
00:40:47,994 --> 00:40:50,862
尊敬的法官大人 Pride探员和Hamilton市长
Your Honor, Agent Pride and Mayor Hamilton

913
00:40:50,864 --> 00:40:52,163
相处的不是很愉快
don't exactly get along.

914
00:40:52,165 --> 00:40:53,698
那又和这事有什么关系
And what does that have to do with this?

915
00:40:53,700 --> 00:40:56,434
因为市长听说发生的事情之后
Because when the mayor heard about what happened,

916
00:40:56,436 --> 00:40:59,337
他叫了督察长开始新的调查
he asked the inspector general to open an investigation.

917
00:40:59,339 --> 00:41:01,906
报复我调查他的事儿
Retribution for my investigating him.

918
00:41:01,908 --> 00:41:03,741
-纯属推测 -说的跟真的一样
- Conjecture. - Like hell it is!

919
00:41:03,743 --> 00:41:04,742
够了
Enough.

920
00:41:04,744 --> 00:41:06,311
你们俩可以晚些继续吵
You two can argue about this later.

921
00:41:06,313 --> 00:41:08,379
但这没有改变事实
But it doesn't change the facts.

922
00:41:09,482 --> 00:41:11,616
你有大麻烦了 年轻的女士
You're in serious trouble, young lady.

923
00:41:11,618 --> 00:41:12,750
因为在我眼里
Because as far as I'm concerned,

924
00:41:12,752 --> 00:41:14,786
你没有说实话
you're not telling me the truth.

925
00:41:14,788 --> 00:41:17,588
你有最后一次机会
You have one last chance.

926
00:41:17,590 --> 00:41:20,792
我想知道你为什么没有逮捕 Nadine Bancroft
I want to know why you didn't arrest Nadine Bancroft,

927
00:41:20,794 --> 00:41:22,860
我想知道她在哪儿
and I want to know where she is,

928
00:41:22,862 --> 00:41:25,196
否则我要判你伪证罪
or I'm gonna charge you with perjury

929
00:41:25,198 --> 00:41:27,732
以及轻视法庭
and hold you in contempt.

930
00:41:27,734 --> 00:41:29,667
你明白吗
Do you understand?

931
00:41:34,541 --> 00:41:36,975
Karen Karen 等等 等等
Karen, Karen, come on, come on.

932
00:41:36,977 --> 00:41:39,143
你为什么这么做
Why are you doing this?

933
00:41:39,145 --> 00:41:40,378
别怪我 Dwayne
Don't blame me, Dwayne.

934
00:41:40,380 --> 00:41:41,846
你探员自找的
Your agent brought this on herself.

935
00:41:41,848 --> 00:41:43,314
我只是做本职工作
I'm just doing my job.

936
00:41:43,316 --> 00:41:45,450
是啊 更像是执行Hamilton的命令
Yeah, more like doing Hamilton's bidding.

937
00:41:45,452 --> 00:41:47,952
没想到你也是和市长同一阵营的
Didn't realize that you were in the mayor's pocket, too.

938
00:41:47,954 --> 00:41:49,153
你知道这不是真的
You know that's not true.

939
00:41:49,155 --> 00:41:50,188
是吗
Do I?

940
00:41:50,190 --> 00:41:51,422
底线是
Bottom line:

941
00:41:51,424 --> 00:41:53,658
你的探员搞砸了 Hamilton反扑了
your agent screwed up, and Hamilton pounced.

942
00:41:53,660 --> 00:41:56,728
我警告过你 如果他发现窃听一事的后果
I warned you what would happen if he found out about the wire.

943
00:41:56,730 --> 00:41:58,029
没什么我能做的
There's nothing I could do.

944
00:41:58,031 --> 00:41:59,364
这不是真的
That's not true.

945
00:41:59,366 --> 00:42:03,634
你让他开了场 现在你必须接受事实
You gave him the opening, now you have to live with it.

946
00:42:06,973 --> 00:42:09,040
刚发生了什么 King
What just happened, King?

947
00:42:09,776 --> 00:42:11,009
Percy呢
Where's Percy?

948
00:42:15,782 --> 00:42:17,648
他们要带她去监狱
They're taking her to jail.

